{"tid":1456010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場陰謀論 自行判斷風險留或走","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:00:32.000Z","uid":89139,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4fb1bba757c5ff28d90291515f7382140c3b8eaa","tid":1456010,"uid":89139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:37:02.000Z","msg":"理性分析<br />\n1. 根據機管局航班資訊最後一班離境航班大約為六點<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongairport.com/tc/flights/departures/passenger.page\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongairport.com%2Ftc%2Fflights%2Fdepartures%2Fpassenger.page&d=nSJvRvahoV7vX7tkwZxFznpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=7f71543c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongairport.com/tc/flights/departures/passenger.page</a><br />\n目標已達成，等航班恢復再去機場上機/接親友都未遲<br />\n<br />\n2. 航空公司職員已疏散<br />\n<br />\n3. 大量狗隻已入機場<br />\n<br />\n4. 政府已經無所不用其極<br />\n<br />\n請自行判斷風險留/走<br />\n<br />\n陰謀論<br />\n<br />\n如果真係斷網，封左東涌出口，停左機鐵，強行捉晒所有人包括記者遊客上車再經港珠澳大橋送中既話，只可以話唔係無可能"},{"pid":"0219bc3359dae4dc99ea1319d0ff8f65ed0c1f2d","tid":1456010,"uid":89139,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:40:56.000Z","msg":"自推 衡量風險留或走 如需徹離 建議徹至東涌/葵景/香港/青衣站待命"},{"pid":"25744548817ce8675789d55f39d82d5099b27c51","tid":1456010,"uid":123898,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:41:12.000Z","msg":"1. 我哋目的係向外宣傳，冇機冇旅客，等於冇宣傳<br />\n<br />\n2. 我哋目的可能係癱瘓機場，依家所有班機都取消，已經癱瘓咗機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日達到目標咗架喇，唔走等比啲鬼伏你?</span><br />\n<br />\n善用不推文"},{"pid":"38fd55fc23329d140d9d49452257ce41f4516e3c","tid":1456010,"uid":89139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:42:29.000Z","msg":"自推 衡量風險留或走 如需徹離 建議徹至東涌/葵景/香港/青衣站待命"},{"pid":"f50baccc94f3cfbf6deb054d39a08a529f183a22","tid":1456010,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:42:31.000Z","msg":"無哂遊客人質<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-